HEADWORD: Bestick
<hw>Be*stick"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <vmorph>[<pos>imp. &
p. p.</pos> <conjf>Bestuck</conjf> <pr>(<?/)</pr>; <pos>p. pr. & vb.
n.</pos> <conjf>Besticking</conjf>.]</vmorph> <def>To stick over, as
with sharp points pressed in; to mark by infixing points or spots here
and there; to pierce.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Truth shall retire⟦br⟧
<qex>Bestuck</qex> with slanderous darts.</q>
<rj><qau>Milton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Bestill</ent>⟦br⟧
